'''''Pantheon''''' ni filime ngufi y’igifaransa yo muri 2017 iyobowe na Ange-Régis Hounkpatin ikorwa na Myrina Mané kuri TS Productions. <ref>http://augohr.de/catalogue/pantheon</ref> Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo William Edimo mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Bass Dhem, Sophia Elisabeth na Hugo Marí. <ref>https://en.unifrance.org/movie/44780/pantheon</ref> Filime irazenguruka Saloman, umushoferi wa tagisi wimyaka 35 akaba umuhungu wumwimukira wa Bénin.<ref>https://en.unifrance.org/movie/44780/pantheon</ref><ref>http://www.africine.org/film/pantheon/20114</ref>

Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku ya 22 Kamena 2017 mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya Palm Springs, muri [[Amerika]]. Iyi filime yakiriwe neza kandi ihitwamo kumugaragaro kugirango yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema nyafurika 2017, iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Atlanta 2018 na Filmfest Dresden 2018<ref>http://www.africapt-festival.fr/films-2018/pantheon-de-ange-regis-hounkpatin/</ref>. Filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Bridging the Borders muri Palm Springs International Festival ya Filime ngufi 2017. Muri uwo mwaka, filime yakiriye icyubahiro mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Kolkata. <ref>http://tsproductions.fr/film/pantheon-ange-regis-hounkpatin</ref><ref>https://www.fondation-jeanluclagardere.com/archives/2018/ange-regis_hounkpatin_a_realise_le_court_metrage_p</ref>

